    <item>
      <title>三天的贸易战争之后，石油边缘更高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了为期三天的低迷之后，石油升至全球市场，交易员评估了从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的最新关税以及可能的报复性措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 23:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本对特朗普关税协议，日元较弱的希望的反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/japan-stocks-set-to-rebound-on-limited-us-loss-trade-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股票总理·伊斯皮邦（Shigeru Ishiba）与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）之间的呼吁反弹，这激发了对关税协议的希望。]]></description>
